highlights.text: “Dream” by LISA is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Taiwan, up 6 spots at #94.
TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Taiwan. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #1.
“DIA DELÍCIA” by Nakama and ΣP has been on Viral Songs Taiwan the longest, at 74 days straight.
“君とうたう歌 (feat. 櫻井ユキノ)” by TENBLANK and 櫻井ユキノ is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Taiwan at #3.
